  "label": "The Cinderwrit Stockvault",
  "description": "The Cinderwrit Stockvault occupies a low, rectangular chamber behind the Exchange’s ash-scored streetwall, its basalt-and-slagcrete shell lined with riveted ceramite shelving. Lock-cages and stamped bin-trays run in tight ranks beneath lumen strips recessed behind grit filters, keeping illumination steady through storm-driven dust. The floor continues the shop’s vitrified paving, its violet sheen broken by scuff tracks and drain channels cut to catch electrostatic ash. A sealed ledger niche and tagged inventory rails impose strict order amid the city’s constant interference and grit-laden air.",
